name: Subtle Spirits Paper Trail (feat. Michael Beckler)

metadata.name: Paper Trail (feat. Michael Beckler) #1 of 5
metadata.description: PAPER TRAIL features artwork by Michael Beckler. Each NFT includes a signed and numbered archival print of the original, along with a bottle labeled with a piece of rice paper that was cut from the original artwork. Labels will be cut to order, with the remainder of the rice paper from each square given to the NFT holder. Limited to just five (5) editions.
